{"tid":1684118,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國研究機構指出2050年新界西北、西九、東九龍一帶可能會被海水大範圍淹沒！","createTime":"2019-10-31T02:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T06:10:07.000Z","uid":1886,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7af2bdcc6e8d1f239888964a78ee589dede4ea","tid":1684118,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20191031/s00002/1572460470207/美研究-海水上升影響遠超預期-港廣泛受威脅-最新推算-2050西九機場啟德或淹沒\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191031%2Fs00002%2F1572460470207%2F%E7%BE%8E%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E9%81%A0%E8%B6%85%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BB%A3%E6%B3%9B%E5%8F%97%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%8E%A8%E7%AE%97-2050%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%95%9F%E5%BE%B7%E6%88%96%E6%B7%B9%E6%B2%92&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=e27544d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191031%2Fs00002%2F1572460470207%2F%E7%BE%8E%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E9%81%A0%E8%B6%85%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BB%A3%E6%B3%9B%E5%8F%97%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E6%8E%A8%E7%AE%97-2050%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%95%9F%E5%BE%B7%E6%88%96%E6%B7%B9%E6%B2%92&h=0d901530\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20191031/s00002/1572460470207/美研究-海水上升影響遠超預期-港廣泛受威脅-最新推算-2050西九機場啟德或淹沒</a><br />\n<br />\n美國研究機構「氣候中心」（Climate Central）在國際期刊《自然通訊》（Nature Communications）發表最新研究，中心採用了新的地理資訊數碼模型「CoastalDEM」，推算到2050年，全球有3億人口的家園或會低於海水一年一度的最高水位，而以往常用、但較易有誤差的地理模型「SRTM」，所推算出受影響人口為7900萬，換言之，採用新模型推算後，更大面積的陸地將面臨被海水淹沒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20191031/s00007/2b794ce0dbd5146d291f43db2073ee1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20191031%2Fs00007%2F2b794ce0dbd5146d291f43db2073ee1f.jpg&h=9d5a696f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據「氣候中心」的地圖，2050年本港新界西北是水淹「重災區」之一，包括政府視作中長期土地供應重要來源的錦田、洪水橋一帶。此外，根據最新推算，本港多處面對水浸威脅的範圍大幅增加，例如啟德一帶，舊模型只顯示舊機場跑道一帶有水浸風險，但新模型顯示，東九龍一帶包括九龍灣、新蒲崗及九龍城一帶均有水浸風險，另西九、赤鱲角機場等均面臨被淹沒風險。"},{"pid":"7c80e3bee76a05d4a810ec74e816648ea185174c","tid":1684118,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:53:01.000Z","msg":"水上屋有冇得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fc901afd8c795e99e28538415cc08a446b148f","tid":1684118,"uid":3331,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7c80e3bee76a05d4a810ec74e816648ea185174c","tid":1684118,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:53:01.000Z","msg":"水上屋有冇得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc850a3f8f38e89ecb1c58c09b9bfec99429855","tid":1684118,"uid":44171,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:58:01.000Z","msg":"變海景樓, fat fat 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3b27f0bd87d4d9a332c24731a617275814715c","tid":1684118,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dc850a3f8f38e89ecb1c58c09b9bfec99429855","tid":1684118,"uid":44171,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:58:01.000Z","msg":"變海景樓, fat fat 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:59:12.000Z","msg":"東方威尼斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6cf9ce612ec332077df20ae03528e192da20e0","tid":1684118,"uid":315584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/bmCKuDX.gif\" />"},